<article id="faq-calendar">
    <h2>Calendar</h2>

    <h3>How do I see all past meetings?</h3>
    <p>
        Click the "View Past Meetings" link on the main calendar page.
    </p>

    <h3>Can I see a list of all upcoming meetings?</h3>
    <p>
        Yes! Click on the "View Upcoming Meetings" link on the main calendar page.
    </p>

    <h3>Can I create a new event?</h3>
    <p>
        Only an admin or members authorized by an admin can create, edit, or
        delete events.
    </p>

    <h3>How do I RSVP to an event?</h3>
    <p>
        Go to the calendar page by clicking the link in the navigation bar. Then
        find the link to the event on the calendar. The title of the event will
        appear as a link on its corresponding day in the calendar. Once you open
        the event, click on the button saying "Count Me In!".
    </p>

    <h3>How do I see who all is going to an event?</h3>
    <p>
        Open the details of the event just as in <i>How do I RSVP to an event?</i>.
        You will find a list of everyone going on that page. You can also view the
        profile of each alumni going to the event from the event details page.
    </p>
</article>

